                <h1>How the recent racially charged incidents on Duke&#039;s campus relate to previous ones</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/61a538c6-1b82-48c9-9919-8ab710c62164.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Students&#x20;held&#x20;a&#x20;study-in&#x20;at&#x20;the&#x20;Allen&#x20;Building&#x20;on&#x20;Saturday&#x20;afternoon&#x20;to&#x20;demand&#x20;a&#x20;University&#x20;policy&#x20;against&#x20;hate&#x20;speech.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Students held a study-in at the Allen Building on Saturday afternoon to demand a University policy against hate speech.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/bre-bradham">Bre Bradham</a> |
                                                                                                                                The Chronicle
                                                                            </figcaption>
                                </aside>
                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                                                    
                <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/21833ab8-8705-48dd-bfe2-e1f985f7e3da.sized-1000x1000.png?w=50&amp;h=50&amp;auto=format&amp;mask=ellipse&amp;fit=facearea&amp;facepad=2.5" class="author-image float-left pr-2" />
                                                        <div class="pt-1">
        
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/ben-leonard">Ben Leonard</a>
                            | <a href="https://twitter.com/Ben___Leonard" target="_blank">@Ben___Leonard</a>
                                            </div>
            
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">April 30, 2018 | 2:23am EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2018/04/how-the-recent-racism-on-dukes-campus-relates-to-previous-incidents" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
